movie_name: The Pembrokeshire Murders: Catching the Gameshow Killer
short_description: The real-life story behind the ITV drama The Pembrokeshire Murders. For the first time, all the key people who brought serial killer John Cooper to justice reveal their role in this extraordinary case.

movie_name: River's End: California's Latest Water War
short_description: A documentary that reveals California's struggle over who gets fresh water, and how moneyed interests game the system. Battling over uncertain water supplies heralds an impending crisis - not just in California, but around the world.
